<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Proses Pembayaran - Hotel De Luna</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #2c2c2c;
      --accent-color: #d4a373;
      --bg-color: #fcf8f1;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text-muted: #666;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg-color);
      color: var(--primary-color);
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .payment-container {
      background: var(--white);
      max-width: 450px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    .divider {
      width: 50px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--accent-color);
      margin: 0 auto 30px;
    }

    .bank-info {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px dashed var(--accent-color);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .bank-info p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .account-number {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--accent-color);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .form-group {
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    input[type="text"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    input[type="text"]:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    button {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--primary-color);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background: #000;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="payment-container">
    <h2>Pembayaran</h2>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Silakan lakukan transfer ke rekening berikut:</p>
    
    <div class="bank-info">
      <p><strong>Bank ABC</strong></p>
      <span class="account-number">1234 5678 90</span>
      <p>a.n <strong>Hotel De Luna</strong></p>
    </div>

    <form action="/booking/konfirmasi" method="POST">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="payment_code">Kode Transaksi / Bukti Pembayaran</label>
        <input type="text" id="payment_code" name="payment_code" placeholder="Contoh: TRX-99821X" required>
      </div>
      
      <button type="submit">Konfirmasi Pembayaran</button>
    </form>

    <p class="note">Pastikan nominal transfer sudah sesuai dengan harga kamar. Proses verifikasi biasanya memakan waktu 5-10 menit.</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>